##If you want to stay for longer

You may be eligible for a [Sportsperson visa (T2)](https://www.gov.uk/sportsperson-visa) to work as an elite sportsperson or coach. It's more expensive than the Temporary Worker - Creative and Sporting visa (T5).

###Eligibility

The eligibility criteria include:

+ having a job offer
+ being endorsed by your sport's governing body - you must be an elite sportsperson or coach at highest level of your profession internationally
+ usually proving that you can speak and understand English

